@startuml
title Collaboration Diagram 

left to right direction
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam nodesep 80
skinparam ranksep 90
skinparam shadowing false

object ":CheckoutPage" as UI
object ":CheckoutController" as C
object ":OrderService" as S
object ":InventoryService" as I
object ":PaymentGateway" as P

' ---- hidden links ONLY to stabilize layout (no arrows shown) ----
UI -[hidden]-> C
C  -[hidden]-> S
S  -[hidden]-> I
I  -[hidden]-> P

' ---- messages (keep labels short to avoid overlap) ----
UI -> C : 1 submitOrder
C  -> S : 1.1 placeOrder
S  -> I : 1.1.1 reserve
S  -> P : 1.1.2 authorize
P --> S : 1.1.3 authResult
I --> S : 1.1.4 reservationId
S --> C : 1.2 confirmation
C --> UI : 1.3 showConfirmation

note bottom of UI
Params:
- submitOrder(cart, customerInfo)
- authorize(amount, paymentToken)
end note

@enduml
